=== Noun ===
'''bear''' (plural '''[[bears]]''')

# A large carnivorous mammal, related to the dog and racoon, having shaggy hair, very small tails and flat feet.
# {{colloquial}} A bear, or any of various animals that resemble a bear, including [[koala]]s, [[panda]]s and [[sloth]]s.  <!-- FWIW, pandas are actually in the family Ursidae -->
# {{finance}} An [[investor]] who sells in anticipation of falling prices.
# {{colloquial}} A problem that is very difficult to solve.
# {{slang}} A large hairy man, especially one who is [[gay]].

